Package: coziR
Type: Package
Title: Conditional Neighborhood Preference Scores
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chiara", "Schiller", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Computes conditional neighborhood preference scores for cell-cell
    interactions using k-nearest neighbors, radius-based, or Delaunay
    neighborhoods. Includes neighborhood quantification, conditional
    normalization, conditional cell ratios, and permutation-based z-scores.
